<subSubSection id="2BF24ACA1F54FFAFFF27FEECFBC43194" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" type="key">
<key id="17794E701F54FFAFFF27FEECFBC43194" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<keyStep id="D81C01E41F54FFAFFF27FEECFBC53290" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<paragraph id="635719411F54FFAFFF27FEECFBC43222" blockId="31.[189,1136,216,660]" box="[189,1134,268,293]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<keyLead id="D819BA741F54FFAFFF27FEECFBC43222" box="[189,1134,268,293]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
1. Limbe lancéolé de 10-15 × 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFE60FEECFDEE3223" box="[506,580,269,293]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="cm" value="2.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.0">2-3 cm</quantity>
, subcoriace; axes inflorescentiels non verruqueux ...... 2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F54FFAFFF27FECBFBC53290" blockId="31.[189,1136,216,660]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<keyLead id="D819BA741F54FFAFFF27FECBFBC53290" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
— Limbe subelliptique à oblong, oblancéolé ou spatulé, de 10-25 × 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFC08FEC8FC753246" box="[914,991,297,321]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="cm" value="5.5" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="3.0">3-8 cm</quantity>
, coriace; axes inflorescentiels manifestement verruqueux; inflorescences pouvant être très amples et étalées; fleurs de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFE0DFE83FDAB327D" box="[407,513,354,378]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.5" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="mm" value="3.75" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.5">3,5-4 mm</quantity>
, à ornementation glanduleuse généralement très visible sur le sec, à pédicelle long de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFE40FE9EFD843290" box="[474,558,383,407]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="mm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3-4 mm</quantity>
...................................... 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F54FFAFFCA4FE61FBBF3290" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[830,1045,383,407]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="storezii" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F54FFAFFCA4FE61FC343290" box="[830,926,384,407]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">T. storezii</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F54FFAFFBBAFE61FBC53290" box="[1056,1135,384,407]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="D81C01E41F54FFAFFF27FE52FBC43194" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<paragraph id="635719411F54FFAFFF27FE52FBC43126" blockId="31.[189,1136,216,660]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<keyLead id="D819BA741F54FFAFFF27FE52FBC43126" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
2. Pédicelles floraux longs de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFD9BFE52FDFC32CD" box="[513,598,435,459]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="mm" value="6.5" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="5.0">5-8 mm</quantity>
; sépales ovales, longs de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFCC7FE52FC3732CD" box="[861,925,435,459]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="mm" value="1.0">1 mm</quantity>
environ; axes inflorescentiels marqués de très fins sillons; limbe marqué de ponctuations glanduleuses, à nervation secondaire assez régulière, avec 10-15 paires de nervures, se détachant de la nervure axiale suivant un angle d’environ 45° .................... 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F54FFAFFCC9FDEBFBC43126" authority="Guillaumin" authorityName="Guillaumin" box="[851,1134,521,545]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="colnettianum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F54FFAFFCC9FDEBFC453126" box="[851,1007,521,545]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">T. colnettianum</emphasis>
Guillaumin
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F54FFAFFF27FDC7FBC43194" blockId="31.[189,1136,216,660]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
<keyLead id="D819BA741F54FFAFFF27FDC7FBC43194" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">
— Pédicelles floraux longs de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFE75FDC4FDF9313A" box="[495,595,549,573]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="mm" value="1.25" valueMax="1.5" valueMin="1.0">1-1,5 mm</quantity>
; sépales elliptiques longs de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F54FFAFFCF0FDC4FC48313A" box="[874,994,549,573]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.35" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="1.2" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" unit="mm" value="1.35" valueMax="1.5" valueMin="1.2">1,2-1,5 mm</quantity>
; axes inflorescentiels presque lisses; limbe sans ponctuation glanduleuse apparente, à nervation secondaire assez lâche et irrégulière, les nervures secondaires se détachant de la nervure axiale suivant un angle inférieur à 45° ................. 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F54FFAFFDB0FD9DFCF53193" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[554,863,636,660]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="brevipedicellatum" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F54FFAFFDB0FD9DFD413193" box="[554,747,636,660]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">T. brevipedicellatum</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F54FFAFFCF2FD9DFC1C3194" box="[872,950,636,659]" pageId="31" pageNumber="310" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F54FFAFFC25FD9DFBC43194" box="[959,1134,636,660]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="310">incomplete cognita</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
